name: NSBatchInsertRequestResultType
desc: Result types for a batch-insertion request.

items.name: case statusOnly
items.desc: A value that indicates that the return type is a Boolean value representing whether the batch-insertion request succeeded.

items.name: case objectIDs
items.desc: A value that indicates the return type is an array of object IDs that corresponds to the inserted rows.

items.name: case count
items.desc: A value that indicates that the return type is the number of inserted rows.
